HEADWORD: Frank-fee
<hw>Frank"-fee`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Frank</ets>
free + <ets>fee</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Eng. Law)</fld> <def>A species of
